{"id": 1078, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x淘宝】 哪些时刻你觉得自己的创造力爆表？", "description": "生命中总有这样的时刻，想拍着自己的肩膀大声称赞：好样的！（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 1776, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160720161210etAZd4KsMOg6vxWF.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-22T03:14:05Z", "options": [{"id": 100485, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687570}, {"id": 100496, "content": "造人的时候………", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679875}, {"id": 100504, "content": "公众号精选评论被赞到前排被朋友看到", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133678}, {"id": 100530, "content": "吃完饭，再喝一杯饮料，再吃一块蛋糕，再吃一份水果，再…", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 491746}, {"id": 100608, "content": "虽然一道不会但还是写满。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601802}, {"id": 101376, "content": "追女孩的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690182}, {"id": 100609, "content": "看别人的创造过程或者听别人吹牛的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244502}, {"id": 100610, "content": "做物理题的时候，觉得脑洞创造了连自己都不敢相信的世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688240}, {"id": 100612, "content": "周遭人不屑你自诩的big idea", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687930}, {"id": 100613, "content": "对女友撒谎的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687930}, {"id": 100614, "content": "小知了今年已两次光顾我家，太奇妙了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688243}, {"id": 100615, "content": "和朋友聊天，忽然就脑洞大开，想象着他们一个个很滑稽的样子，自己哈哈笑，他们问怎么回事，我说没啥。", "image": "img/option/option/201607222338311bMCKyecfEhOdrj3.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688252}, {"id": 100616, "content": "梦里w", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685263}, {"id": 100618, "content": "对一件事做了10个字的精辟总结", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637065}, {"id": 100619, "content": "明天早上就要交作品的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688259}, {"id": 100621, "content": "讲真，做梦的时候。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688264}, {"id": 100626, "content": "突然想把某件事做到很好的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129641}, {"id": 100627, "content": "夜深人静的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688282}, {"id": 102419, "content": "学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694484}, {"id": 100628, "content": "神吐槽的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593560}, {"id": 104212, "content": "突破专业上的一个瓶颈的一瞬间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701823}, {"id": 100629, "content": "觉得自己不是正常人…?有各种超常技能…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683013}, {"id": 101397, "content": "两个朋友在一起玩尺度大的游戏，被我做成gif", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690206}, {"id": 100630, "content": "20岁以前", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 64721}, {"id": 100631, "content": "当用听懂的一句歌词搜出一整首歌的时候。 当终于明白语言的存在是为了人们表达自己的时候。当发觉一个鲜有人知的好歌者的时候。当为他人带来微笑时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688306}, {"id": 100632, "content": "躺在床上睡着之前?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485679}, {"id": 100633, "content": "躺在床上无聊 又睡不着的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688322}, {"id": 100634, "content": "在看英语考研阅读理解的时候～", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688323}, {"id": 100896, "content": "撒谎的时候", "image": null, "praise_count"